### How to establish a WiFi connection with the UWN200

1) after installing drivers, insert USB adapter and reboot BBB

2) Follow the instructions in 
"Tutorial_installing-Compact-USB-Wifi-Adapter-on-BBB.pdf"

3) To actually connect, use VNC server and press the "network-button" in 
top right corner of screen. Choose the correct network you want to 
connect to, then on your router, turn on WPS-service (a button, or 
online somewhere to start a WPS process). Then in angstrom, choose the 
network and simply press "connect" and it will auto-setup everything

4) The wifi should now work and should automatically start upon boot
